title: Bug 116564: Incorrect title in hyperlink builder
OB: When clicking on the 'OK' button and then reopening the hyperlink builder, the actual title displayed is 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the hyperlink builder. 2. Click on the 'OK' button. 3. Close the hyperlink builder. 4. Reopen the hyperlink builder and observe the title.
